# Artifacto — code editing workflow

## When you edit a file

After changes — remind the user which artifact needs updating:
"Artifact for `<ModuleName>` may be stale. Run: Artifacto → Regenerate Artifact for Current File"

## Signs an artifact needs regeneration

- Function signatures changed
- New imports or dependencies added
- Module was renamed, split, or merged
- New public functions added

## Artifact status indicators (visible in status bar)

- `✓` green = artifact is current
- `⚠` yellow = file changed, artifact needs update
- `✗` missing = no artifact yet, consider initializing
